summary: All the parts of my "Skyrim The Movie" series of images from 3 about centuries ago, in one pack for you to download and use as desktop wallpapers if you like!
descriptionHtml:
[font=verdana][color=yellow][size=1]So, I don't know if anyone will remember but about 3 centuries ago I made a series of images here on the Nexus called "Skyrim The Movie", tracking the adventures of my first Skyrim character, Talea of Anvil.

I just found them on my hard drive, so if you like this look as much as I do, you can now download them.

They are all high quality 1600x900 j-pegs (originals are long gone I'm afraid), but work really well at any resolution due to the highly stylized look.

And, if there is enough interest, I may do a new series in this style...[/font][/color][/size]
author: Demidekidasu
